statement.para:
For a matrix \Mtrx{A} of size (m,n),

				rankformula for matrices

					Rank formula for matrices



\begin{array}{rcl}
n & = & \Rnk{ \Mtrx{ A } } + \Dim{ \NllSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } \\
  & = & \Dim{ \RowSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } + \Dim{ \NllSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } \\
  & = & \Dim{ \ColSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } + \Dim{ \NllSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } }
\end{array}

math.display.latex:

\begin{array}{rcl}
n & = & \Rnk{ \Mtrx{ A } } + \Dim{ \NllSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } \\
  & = & \Dim{ \RowSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } + \Dim{ \NllSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } \\
  & = & \Dim{ \ColSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } } + \Dim{ \NllSp{ \Mtrx{ A } } }
\end{array}
